channel.title: 508 HD Ip Changer, need help!
channel.description:
I got the one that says "508 Ip Changer" and you open it to get another folder called "508 HD Client". I think It's called Josh's HD Client or something, but anyway, I open it up and enter the specific IP and all it does is stay at the "Connecting to Update Server.." part. I ran the "build" and it said it couldn't find the specified folder..
I'm no expert but I think that's wrong. :)
I prefer to use the HD Client then an LD (which I'll be using until I'm helped).
Thanks! :D
Edit: Actually, LD Client won't work, same problem with the build.cmd .
